config BR2_PACKAGE_FASTRPC_EXT
	bool "fastrpc"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBYAML
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBBSD
	help
	  Qualcomm FastRPC userspace library and the fastrpc_test
	  validation tool. fastrpc_test exercises CPU<->DSP remote
	  procedure calls by loading a payload onto a coprocessor
	  (e.g. the CDSP), running it and checking the response.

	  Used here to validate the OP-TEE PAS (Peripheral Authentication
	  Service) coprocessor load/reset sequences: a passing run proves
	  OP-TEE brought the coprocessor up correctly.

	  https://github.com/qualcomm/fastrpc
